{"tid":2339392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【疫情下平安夜】尖沙咀海旁人頭湧湧　 市民外出感受節日氣氛","createTime":"2020-12-24T15:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T15:44:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"eae6aa346bddefb9d244fee2feb0317015f9fdf8","tid":2339392,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:03:48.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】疫情下的平安夜，尖沙咀海旁和灣仔利東街人頭湧湧，不少市民外出感受節日氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n在灣仔利東街有璀璨的聖誕燈飾，不少情侶和家庭來感受節日氣氛。有人戴上聖誕頭飾，配以特色口罩，拍照留倩影。在濃厚的節日氣氛下，有情侶隔著口罩情深一吻。<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀海旁亦都很熱鬧，有一家大小出來感受聖誕氣氛，家長為小朋友悉心打扮。警員不時巡邏，提醒市民遵守限聚令。星光大道的地下亦有貼紙，提醒要保持社交距離。<br />\n<br />\n防疫措施下，酒吧要關閉，昔日佳節人頭湧湧的蘭桂芳，今年顯得格外冷清。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=417841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417841&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt%2FRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=f898943a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417841&h=3782465a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=417841</a>"},{"pid":"eab92fa26dc4c971cfa44f34002091ef0434c84b","tid":2339392,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CaDuO4t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCaDuO4t.jpg&h=3365458e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c48eb6819c4310020fdea804952e2fab820bd121","tid":2339392,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:22:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7f7b2213a9f2b44fde3866608ec015f823197cc","tid":2339392,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c48eb6819c4310020fdea804952e2fab820bd121","tid":2339392,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eab92fa26dc4c971cfa44f34002091ef0434c84b","tid":2339392,"uid":361751,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T15:04:32.